      "full_name": "Public Joint Stock Company “Stavropol Radio Plant Signal”",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "PJSC “Stavropol Radio Plant Signal” is one of the main manufacturers of radio-electronic devices for the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation. It belongs to the Rostec State Corporation. Armed Forces of the Russian Federation use devices produced by PJSC “Stavropol Radio Plant Signal” such as remote-control platforms for PKT tank machine guns in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. PJSC “Stavropol Radio Plant Signal” upgraded the machine gun remote-control platform for the control of a 7,62 mm tank machine gun, designed in 2023, on direct request from the Russian military. In addition, PJSC “Stavropol Radio Plant Signal”, together with the Russian Engineering Union and the North Caucasus Federal University, runs a training centre for highly qualified specialists in the mechanical engineering industry.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}